1
00:03:09,622 --> 00:03:11,557
(Phone Vibrates)

2
00:03:12,825 --> 00:03:13,526
Yes, Mom?

3
00:03:13,527 --> 00:03:15,007
Have you arrived in Phuket yet, dear?

4
00:03:17,163 --> 00:03:17,997
Yes, I'm here.

5
00:03:17,998 --> 00:03:21,066
Why didn’t you tell me?

6
00:03:21,067 --> 00:03:24,370
I was worried, you know.

7
00:03:24,471 --> 00:03:25,216
Mom...

8
00:03:26,105 --> 00:03:27,673
I just got off the plane.

9
00:03:27,674 --> 00:03:29,441
As long as everything worked out, that’s all that matters.

10
00:03:29,442 --> 00:03:31,109
And don’t forget.

11
00:03:31,110 --> 00:03:32,912
Don’t do anything risky.

12
00:03:34,047 --> 00:03:36,540
You don't have to be worried, I'm already here.

13
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:39,216
And also, nothing is gonna happen, Mom.

14
00:03:39,832 --> 00:03:45,203
Don’t forget to go to the shrine like the feng shui master told you.

15
00:03:45,525 --> 00:03:47,427
Have you met Sang yet?

16
00:03:55,168 --> 00:03:56,302
Hey Mom? I gotta go now.

17
00:05:29,608 --> 00:05:34,113
Actually, life here isn’t as bad as I’d imagined.

18
00:06:12,918 --> 00:06:15,020
Hey! You!

19
00:06:16,785 --> 00:06:21,088
How could you step on another man's crown jewels?

20
00:06:21,409 --> 00:06:22,811
I... I'm so sorry!

21
00:06:24,306 --> 00:06:25,063
Wait!

22
00:06:25,461 --> 00:06:27,796
You're not even thinking of apologizing?

23
00:06:28,103 --> 00:06:29,104
You!

24
00:06:32,087 --> 00:06:33,255
You got no manners!

25
00:06:42,077 --> 00:06:43,678
I already apologized.

26
00:06:43,679 --> 00:06:45,581
But you're the one that didn't listen.

27
00:06:49,651 --> 00:06:52,621
At that volume, how would I have heard you?

28
00:06:54,135 --> 00:06:55,229
Well, I already tried apologizing.

29
00:06:55,574 --> 00:06:56,851
You just didn't listen carefully.

30
00:06:57,125 --> 00:07:00,828
Well, next time, could you please try to speak louder?

31
00:07:00,829 --> 00:07:02,331
That would be great.

32
00:07:02,831 --> 00:07:03,899
Then...

33
00:07:05,433 --> 00:07:07,101
next time...

34
00:07:07,349 --> 00:07:08,550
please listen carefully.

35
00:07:09,123 --> 00:07:11,359
That would be great too.

36
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,648
Serves you right!

37
00:07:39,741 --> 00:07:41,076
Hey, sis.

38
00:07:41,376 --> 00:07:42,376
Where have you been?

39
00:07:45,234 --> 00:07:46,347
Well...

40
00:07:46,348 --> 00:07:47,716
I got here since early morning.

41
00:07:47,929 --> 00:07:50,698
I thought coming home would be too boring..

42
00:07:50,786 --> 00:07:52,020
so I went to the beach.

43
00:07:52,988 --> 00:07:53,988
The beach?

44
00:07:55,457 --> 00:07:56,457
Hey!

45
00:07:56,992 --> 00:07:58,660
What are you getting riled up about?

46
00:08:00,796 --> 00:08:03,665
A girl being this loud, when will you ever find a boyfriend?

47
00:08:03,865 --> 00:08:04,865
Sang.

48
00:08:05,133 --> 00:08:08,103
And didn't you say you were going out with a client?

49
00:08:08,510 --> 00:08:10,430
That's because I was waiting to pick up Kim, Dad

50
00:08:10,646 --> 00:08:11,813
I was waiting for ages,

51
00:08:11,993 --> 00:08:13,273
I called, and he didn't pick up.

52
00:08:13,716 --> 00:08:16,420
Next time, if you're going anywhere, tell us!

53
00:08:16,445 --> 00:08:18,213
We got actual jobs to do!

54
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,761
Well..

55
00:08:19,974 --> 00:08:22,243
..no one told me that someone was picking me up.

56
00:08:24,152 --> 00:08:25,320
Seriously, Kim..

57
00:08:26,101 --> 00:08:27,636
why'd your mom send you here?

58
00:08:27,936 --> 00:08:29,004
About that..

59
00:08:29,204 --> 00:08:30,638
Mom told you already you, didn't she?

60
00:08:30,699 --> 00:08:32,000
The quarter life crisis?

61
00:08:32,301 --> 00:08:35,304
Women are so gullible.

62
00:08:35,764 --> 00:08:36,897
These kinds of things..

63
00:08:36,898 --> 00:08:39,233
if you don't believe, then don't talk ill of them, Dad.

64
00:08:39,234 --> 00:08:41,903
These rich people types are all superstitious.

65
00:08:42,337 --> 00:08:43,337
And another thing..

66
00:08:43,478 --> 00:08:47,682
I don't think being a woman means you're gullible.

67
00:08:48,249 --> 00:08:51,279
Even amulet dealers are men, aren't they?

68
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:52,580
Siw!

69
00:08:52,814 --> 00:08:54,814
Will there be a day where you don't argue with me?

70
00:08:54,950 --> 00:08:56,751
Act like the daughter I raised you to be!

71
00:08:56,818 --> 00:08:58,786
Why does my life have to be like this?

72
00:08:58,787 --> 00:09:01,790
No son, can't rely on either of my daughters..

73
00:09:02,457 --> 00:09:04,937
If there’s anything, be there to help your sister, understand?

74
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,560
It's okay..

75
00:09:06,695 --> 00:09:08,029
I can do it myself.

76
00:09:08,964 --> 00:09:10,532
Look at my daughters...

77
00:09:12,734 --> 00:09:13,734
Siw!

78
00:09:14,129 --> 00:09:15,731
Take your cousin to his room!

79
00:09:17,478 --> 00:09:19,213
Let's go go.

80
00:09:47,836 --> 00:09:48,676
What you looking at?

81
00:09:50,539 --> 00:09:53,174
You look good now that you're older.

82
00:09:55,777 --> 00:09:57,112
What's with you?

83
00:09:57,779 --> 00:10:01,382
Well, when you moved to Bangkok, I was still really young

84
00:10:01,383 --> 00:10:03,117
I can barely remember anything

85
00:10:03,118 --> 00:10:05,720
not even what your face looks like.

86
00:10:09,791 --> 00:10:10,791
Alright, alright...

87
00:10:11,026 --> 00:10:12,227
I'm gonna unpack.

88
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,399
Wait...

89
00:10:21,803 --> 00:10:22,803
What else?

90
00:10:24,173 --> 00:10:25,841
You're really here for the inheritence?

91
00:10:48,196 --> 00:10:49,196
Just kidding!

92
00:10:50,098 --> 00:10:51,466
Don't worry..

93
00:10:52,227 --> 00:10:55,230
I'm only here for another 364 days.

94
00:10:56,237 --> 00:10:57,706
Once the year is complete,

95
00:10:58,540 --> 00:11:00,909
I'm going back to Bangkok.

96
00:11:02,177 --> 00:11:03,177
That's good.

97
00:11:03,478 --> 00:11:06,481
Because if you're gonna mess with Dad and Sang,

98
00:11:07,315 --> 00:11:09,483
I think you should take your time and work,

99
00:11:09,484 --> 00:11:12,454
.. that might be easier.

100
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:16,424
Then...

101
00:11:17,225 --> 00:11:19,027
What do you think I should do?

102
00:11:20,061 --> 00:11:24,065
Live stream and talk to myself day by day?

103
00:11:24,199 --> 00:11:25,667
Kinda like..

104
00:11:26,935 --> 00:11:28,670
Hello!

105
00:11:28,703 --> 00:11:29,838
It's Siw!

106
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:31,573
You...

107
00:11:31,574 --> 00:11:33,307
know that I'm an influencer?

108
00:11:33,308 --> 00:11:34,909
Are you following?

109
00:11:36,077 --> 00:11:37,077
Well..

110
00:11:37,312 --> 00:11:38,312
No.

111
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:41,216
I was just... scrolling through.

112
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:42,951
Kay!

113
00:11:43,184 --> 00:11:44,252
I'm outta here!

114
00:11:45,587 --> 00:11:47,555
I'm actually pretty famous!

115
00:12:44,345 --> 00:12:52,345
(Phone Vibrates)

116
00:13:02,163 --> 00:13:03,331
Yes, Mom?

117
00:13:03,398 --> 00:13:06,867
Uncle told me you’d arrived but still refused to come home.

118
00:13:06,868 --> 00:13:10,772
Do you know how worried you’re making your mother?

119
00:13:11,539 --> 00:13:12,841
Mom...

120
00:13:13,455 --> 00:13:15,056
you don't have to worry, okay?

121
00:13:15,671 --> 00:13:18,040
I can take care of myself.

122
00:13:19,394 --> 00:13:21,162
Once the year is up...

123
00:13:21,456 --> 00:13:23,218
I'll be back to take care of you again.

124
00:13:25,754 --> 00:13:26,855
Mom?

125
00:13:28,456 --> 00:13:29,724
I love you.

126
00:14:04,993 --> 00:14:06,161
- Daiji..
- Yeah..

127
00:14:06,394 --> 00:14:07,796
Prepare more food tomorrow, okay?

128
00:14:08,863 --> 00:14:10,665
We got guests in almost 10 rooms.

129
00:14:11,232 --> 00:14:13,234
- Almost fully booked
- Okay, can do.

130
00:14:16,704 --> 00:14:19,140
Make some Kanom Jeen too, and also..

131
00:14:19,707 --> 00:14:21,109
fish balls...

132
00:14:22,143 --> 00:14:25,146
maybe some lobster, around 10 kilos...

133
00:14:25,213 --> 00:14:27,282
Oh, okay...

134
00:14:33,521 --> 00:14:35,557
And where did Tao Sor go?

135
00:14:38,092 --> 00:14:39,227
Probably...

136
00:14:39,361 --> 00:14:40,929
out to draw outside...

137
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:42,627
Huh?

138
00:14:42,738 --> 00:14:44,153
He's drawing outside?

139
00:14:44,833 --> 00:14:46,266
Who did he go with?

140
00:14:46,267 --> 00:14:48,269
Who let him go?

141
00:14:51,873 --> 00:14:53,874
I already told him..

142
00:14:53,955 --> 00:14:56,124
to wait for me to get the stock ready first

143
00:14:56,230 --> 00:14:57,464
but he wouldn't take it

144
00:14:57,492 --> 00:14:59,493
said he could go himself.

145
00:14:59,708 --> 00:15:01,810
He wouldn't let me tell you too!

146
00:15:10,191 --> 00:15:11,993
Tao Sor!

147
00:15:12,621 --> 00:15:14,156
Yes?

148
00:15:15,697 --> 00:15:16,764
Where have you been?

149
00:15:18,399 --> 00:15:19,834
Umm...

150
00:15:20,401 --> 00:15:22,036
I was outside

151
00:15:22,984 --> 00:15:24,819
I told you already, right?

152
00:15:25,373 --> 00:15:27,575
If you're going anywhere, you need to tell me.

153
00:15:31,179 --> 00:15:31,980
Okay, okay...

154
00:15:32,013 --> 00:15:33,013
go paint.

155
00:16:56,672 --> 00:16:57,619
How you been, Tao Sor?

156
00:16:58,307 --> 00:17:00,276
You took the car for a trip?

157
00:17:03,346 --> 00:17:04,342
This is Dr. Kluen

158
00:17:05,248 --> 00:17:08,084
he's been taking care of your conditon all this time.

159
00:17:16,765 --> 00:17:19,100
Why...

160
00:17:21,564 --> 00:17:23,666
...do I feel like I've seen this in my dreams?

161
00:17:26,168 --> 00:17:28,804
These pictures you drew...

162
00:17:29,438 --> 00:17:33,142
must be your dreams you remembered from each night.

163
00:17:34,143 --> 00:17:36,012
And...

164
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:41,178
...as for the drawings with clear faces

165
00:17:41,203 --> 00:17:43,985
most likely came from you drawing

166
00:17:43,986 --> 00:17:46,655
and wanting to remember them

167
00:17:46,656 --> 00:17:48,356
so you drew them out in detail.

168
00:17:48,357 --> 00:17:49,358
Why...

169
00:17:49,759 --> 00:17:51,727
..can't I remember anything?

170
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:56,198
It's okay, Tao Sor.

171
00:17:56,299 --> 00:17:58,166
You can't remember today,

172
00:17:58,167 --> 00:18:01,170
but tomorrow, you might! Who could tell?

173
00:18:01,637 --> 00:18:04,640
How long have I been like this?

174
00:18:10,413 --> 00:18:13,015
That's not important, Tao Sor!

175
00:18:14,898 --> 00:18:16,132
And...

176
00:18:16,717 --> 00:18:18,821
..will there be a day that I can remember?

177
00:18:22,232 --> 00:18:24,133
But... whatever.

178
00:18:24,627 --> 00:18:27,797
Even if I knew, I'd just forget it all tomorrow.

179
00:18:28,764 --> 00:18:31,767
Isn't it enough for you to be happy with today?

180
00:18:33,481 --> 00:18:35,684
The space for memories...

181
00:18:36,405 --> 00:18:40,476
your family will be filling in those blanks, for what you need to know.

182
00:18:41,210 --> 00:18:43,611
Whether or not you will remember,

183
00:18:43,612 --> 00:18:45,247
I want to let you know

184
00:18:46,682 --> 00:18:49,185
that everyone loves you and cares about you always.

185
00:18:52,521 --> 00:18:53,521
Okay.

186
00:19:05,701 --> 00:19:08,704
There's a large ship booking today, Dad

187
00:19:08,904 --> 00:19:10,420
I was thinking that I'll go too.

188
00:19:11,574 --> 00:19:12,875
Let Gim take care of that!

189
00:19:13,835 --> 00:19:14,970
Put him to work for once

190
00:19:15,297 --> 00:19:16,498
I'll tell him myself.

191
00:19:17,452 --> 00:19:18,787
Don't bother, Dad.

192
00:19:19,081 --> 00:19:21,050
It's my job, I can do it myself.

193
00:19:22,118 --> 00:19:23,118
What about Siw?

194
00:19:24,086 --> 00:19:25,654
Probably not awake yet?

195
00:19:27,917 --> 00:19:28,984
Both of my daughters...

196
00:19:29,111 --> 00:19:30,345
each such a case.

197
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,467
Your nephew's also the same

198
00:19:32,648 --> 00:19:34,150
I can't see much difference.

199
00:19:38,654 --> 00:19:39,789
I've got it!

200
00:19:43,906 --> 00:19:46,542
I'm going to do a 1 day trip here.

201
00:19:47,176 --> 00:19:48,244
What kind of trip?

202
00:19:54,316 --> 00:19:55,417
Taking tourists...

203
00:19:55,418 --> 00:19:57,720
to come learn local cooking.

204
00:20:05,895 --> 00:20:07,797
I'll be back, sis.

205
00:20:17,314 --> 00:20:18,314
Daiji,

206
00:20:18,315 --> 00:20:21,585
could you help me try this?
- Can do!

207
00:20:29,926 --> 00:20:30,900
Woah!

208
00:20:31,234 --> 00:20:32,669
This is on point!

209
00:20:33,402 --> 00:20:35,027
Woah, so delicious!

210
00:20:35,805 --> 00:20:37,373
Good!

211
00:20:42,505 --> 00:20:43,396
Delicious!

212
00:20:54,084 --> 00:20:55,751
You remembered?

213
00:20:55,752 --> 00:20:57,987
That I don't eat spicy foods in the morning.

214
00:20:57,988 --> 00:20:59,188
Oh...

215
00:20:59,189 --> 00:21:02,492
Daiji told me to get Dry Boiled Rice for you.

216
00:21:07,731 --> 00:21:08,932
So I see.

217
00:21:11,468 --> 00:21:13,169
Menu, Sir.

218
00:21:26,381 --> 00:21:27,648
Tell your chef to go ahead.

219
00:21:27,974 --> 00:21:31,278
Anything that your chef makes best.

220
00:22:42,778 --> 00:22:44,079
Excuse me!

221
00:22:51,376 --> 00:22:53,077
Could you bring the owner here?

222
00:22:53,078 --> 00:22:54,813
If you had anything, you can tell me.

223
00:22:55,747 --> 00:22:57,182
I want to talk to the owner.

224
00:22:59,751 --> 00:23:00,751
Okay!

225
00:23:07,659 --> 00:23:08,794
Um, excuse me?

226
00:23:09,227 --> 00:23:10,829
Are there any problems with the food?

227
00:23:21,626 --> 00:23:23,594
You're the owner here?

228
00:23:24,743 --> 00:23:27,144
I'm the one who made this dish for you.

229
00:23:27,145 --> 00:23:29,305
If there's anything you don't like, you could tell me.

230
00:23:30,782 --> 00:23:32,718
So you're a chef, huh?

231
00:23:34,926 --> 00:23:36,561
Good!

232
00:23:36,795 --> 00:23:38,930
Will you be interested in doing a project with me?

233
00:23:45,997 --> 00:23:47,077
Is there anything going on?

234
00:23:47,466 --> 00:23:48,600
So...

235
00:23:49,468 --> 00:23:52,070
I tasted the food here and I feel like the flavour is...

236
00:23:56,341 --> 00:23:57,876
...so delicious!

237
00:23:58,777 --> 00:24:02,214
It made me think about when I was here with my brother when I was young.

238
00:24:02,814 --> 00:24:05,217
So I want to hold a 1 day trip here,

239
00:24:05,584 --> 00:24:07,852
so I can bring tourists to come learn how to cook.

240
00:24:07,853 --> 00:24:10,856
This way, everyone would be able to know your food as well.

241
00:24:15,861 --> 00:24:18,362
If you want something, please come talk to me this way

242
00:24:18,363 --> 00:24:20,197
I'm the one who makes all the decisions here.

243
00:24:20,198 --> 00:24:21,933
We can just talk here!

244
00:24:24,302 --> 00:24:25,941
You've seem to have lost your manners

245
00:24:26,064 --> 00:24:28,665
coming here, doing some weird test

246
00:24:28,690 --> 00:24:31,126
and being delusional thinking you'll do this and that here.

247
00:24:31,743 --> 00:24:33,011
And what do you think?

248
00:24:33,512 --> 00:24:36,213
This is probably better than your resort

249
00:24:36,214 --> 00:24:38,482
in case the tourists who come like it here,

250
00:24:38,483 --> 00:24:39,483
and decide to stay here.

251
00:24:43,989 --> 00:24:45,190
Daiji!

252
00:24:47,392 --> 00:24:48,360
What's up?

253
00:24:48,361 --> 00:24:50,227
I'm letting Daiji look after this project.

254
00:24:50,228 --> 00:24:51,228
No.

255
00:24:51,730 --> 00:24:54,198
I need the chef who made this dish for me

256
00:24:54,199 --> 00:24:56,101
be the one in charge.

257
00:25:00,272 --> 00:25:01,673
What do you think?

258
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:04,280
Are you interested in joining this project with me?

259
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,948
Hey, you don't know anything

260
00:25:10,949 --> 00:25:12,717
better not to get involved.

261
00:25:14,052 --> 00:25:17,054
If you won't take my offer of having Chef Daiji teach,

262
00:25:17,055 --> 00:25:18,589
then you're welcome to leave.

263
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:19,758
Daiji.

264
00:25:20,592 --> 00:25:21,892
Take Tao Sor to go rest.

265
00:25:21,893 --> 00:25:22,794
Okay.

266
00:25:22,795 --> 00:25:24,162
Let's go!

267
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:26,230
Wait!

268
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:38,310
I'd rather hear the answer from the chef's own mouth.

269
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:56,695
I'm going to do this project.

270
00:25:58,163 --> 00:25:59,730
Good! In that case,

271
00:25:59,731 --> 00:26:02,500
Next week I'm going to bring my first tour group here.

272
00:26:04,202 --> 00:26:05,202
As for you...

273
00:26:06,538 --> 00:26:07,538
Next time,

274
00:26:09,207 --> 00:26:10,508
give me a banger.

275
00:26:19,937 --> 00:26:21,439
But really...

276
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:25,232
Letting Tao Sor try something new,

277
00:26:25,536 --> 00:26:26,825
is a good thing, you know?

278
00:26:27,092 --> 00:26:30,395
But I'm afraid that kid is gonna become a problem for Tao Sor.

279
00:26:32,397 --> 00:26:33,670
Why would you worry?

280
00:26:34,466 --> 00:26:37,302
We've taken care of Tao Sor for 10 years already!

281
00:26:37,661 --> 00:26:40,197
We've been through dark moments so many times.

282
00:26:40,672 --> 00:26:43,174
Something as small like this, we'll be able to get through.

283
00:26:58,423 --> 00:26:59,423
Kim!

284
00:27:01,059 --> 00:27:02,593
After being outside all day,

285
00:27:02,594 --> 00:27:03,795
what have you brought back?

286
00:27:11,069 --> 00:27:12,236
I think..

287
00:27:12,237 --> 00:27:15,240
you, can start finding clients for my tour.

288
00:27:15,707 --> 00:27:18,108
Because, I've found a place that teaches cooking.

289
00:27:18,109 --> 00:27:20,011
It's real hot, I'm telling you.

290
00:27:25,116 --> 00:27:26,384
I'm sorry?

291
00:27:27,752 --> 00:27:29,788
Who said I'd find clients for you?

292
00:27:30,956 --> 00:27:32,456
If you're gonna do something yourself,

293
00:27:32,457 --> 00:27:34,392
then be able to do it all!

294
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:40,812
For the only male heir of the clan,

295
00:27:41,879 --> 00:27:43,881
something like this shouldn't be difficult.

296
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:50,275
Okay!

297
00:27:51,376 --> 00:27:53,078
Just wait and see...

298
00:28:20,872 --> 00:28:25,610
(Phone Vibrates)

299
00:28:26,978 --> 00:28:27,879
Yes, Mom?

300
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,781
Have you eaten yet, dear?

301
00:28:31,916 --> 00:28:33,216
Yes, I have.

302
00:28:35,153 --> 00:28:36,820
Oh! Mom?

303
00:28:36,821 --> 00:28:39,757
I went to eat at a place today.

304
00:28:39,758 --> 00:28:40,758
So delicious!

305
00:28:41,059 --> 00:28:43,461
It tasted like my childhood, where..

306
00:28:46,865 --> 00:28:47,866
Uh...

307
00:28:48,299 --> 00:28:48,933
let's just say

308
00:28:48,934 --> 00:28:50,934
it still can't beat the food at Bangkok.

309
00:28:50,935 --> 00:28:54,695
There's tons of great places everywhere in Bangkok, you don;t have to fly down here to Phuket.

310
00:28:57,314 --> 00:29:00,751
Have you gone to the shrine yet?

311
00:29:03,114 --> 00:29:04,515
Yes...

312
00:29:04,516 --> 00:29:06,316
..in about..

313
00:29:06,317 --> 00:29:08,820
2 -3 days I was thinking of going.

314
00:29:09,587 --> 00:29:13,425
The deity there's kind and easygoing, right?

315
00:29:15,026 --> 00:29:16,428
Then..

316
00:29:16,828 --> 00:29:18,696
I'm going to freshen up and go to bed, okay?

317
00:29:19,397 --> 00:29:20,532
That's all.

318
00:29:22,434 --> 00:29:23,434
Good night, Mom.

319
00:29:23,435 --> 00:29:25,737
Good night.

320
00:31:02,474 --> 00:31:03,263
Tao Sor.

321
00:31:05,077 --> 00:31:05,813
My name's Talay

322
00:31:06,667 --> 00:31:07,975
I'm your brother.

323
00:31:09,457 --> 00:31:10,708
Mom and Dad are waiting downstairs.

324
00:31:11,504 --> 00:31:12,681
Get showered quick

325
00:31:13,201 --> 00:31:15,142
I'll show you around the house.

326
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:27,407
Our family runs a resort.

327
00:31:27,408 --> 00:31:29,242
Normally, you'll help out in the kitchen.

328
00:31:29,243 --> 00:31:31,011
You might not remember,

329
00:31:31,012 --> 00:31:34,015
but you make amazing Thai and Chinese food.

330
00:31:36,091 --> 00:31:38,826
As for the other cuisines, Chef Daiji will be in charge

331
00:31:38,851 --> 00:31:41,187
and he'll help you with everything.

332
00:31:43,357 --> 00:31:46,994
So today there will be a tourist couple coming to learn cooking with you.

333
00:31:49,143 --> 00:31:50,710
Huh? With..with me?

334
00:31:52,572 --> 00:31:54,908
It's okay, no need to worry.

335
00:31:55,443 --> 00:31:57,412
Today's menu is Mie Hokkian,

336
00:31:57,536 --> 00:31:59,962
a menu you could make with your eyes closed.

337
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:00,996
Isn't that right?

338
00:32:01,936 --> 00:32:04,272
I do know how to make it,

339
00:32:06,019 --> 00:32:07,354
I don't know how to teach.

340
00:32:09,723 --> 00:32:10,758
What should we do?

341
00:32:11,410 --> 00:32:13,087
This way, follow me!

342
00:32:16,224 --> 00:32:20,360
So ladies and gentlemen, welcome to Siam Cuisine.

343
00:32:20,361 --> 00:32:22,563
The exclusive honeymoon kitchen.

344
00:32:25,065 --> 00:32:26,065
Um...

345
00:32:27,702 --> 00:32:29,370
I might have to ask to cancel for today.

346
00:32:32,173 --> 00:32:33,173
Wait, hey.

347
00:32:33,441 --> 00:32:34,474
How could you do this?

348
00:32:34,475 --> 00:32:35,676
My clients are already here.

349
00:32:40,782 --> 00:32:42,784
All the ingredients are laid out and prepared, no?

350
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:46,821
But our chef isn't ready yet.

351
00:32:47,688 --> 00:32:49,857
If you want Tao Sor, it has to be another day.

352
00:32:50,792 --> 00:32:53,093
But if you're set on today,

353
00:32:53,094 --> 00:32:54,796
I'll have Chef Daiji be the one teaching.

354
00:32:58,332 --> 00:32:59,600
One minute please.

355
00:33:10,211 --> 00:33:11,211
Hey, you.

356
00:33:12,113 --> 00:33:13,113
We're all grown up

357
00:33:13,648 --> 00:33:14,916
have some responsibility.

358
00:33:15,216 --> 00:33:16,984
We talked that day, didn't we?

359
00:33:17,285 --> 00:33:18,653
You made an agreement with me.

360
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:20,555
Why are acting like you don't remember.

361
00:33:23,558 --> 00:33:24,559
Hey, sir.

362
00:33:25,259 --> 00:33:26,727
It's the same either way.

363
00:33:27,286 --> 00:33:28,755
Could you not make this a big deal?

364
00:33:29,897 --> 00:33:30,897
It's okay.

365
00:33:33,086 --> 00:33:34,187
I'll teach.

366
00:33:34,802 --> 00:33:37,004
Okay, that means we're clear?

367
00:33:38,105 --> 00:33:39,674
Sir, Ma'am? Please come inside.

368
00:33:47,815 --> 00:33:49,283
You slice off the shallot,

369
00:33:49,584 --> 00:33:51,886
I want to you to cut it by yourself.

370
00:33:52,286 --> 00:33:53,354
Because.

371
00:33:54,488 --> 00:33:55,669
I want you to stand

372
00:33:56,043 --> 00:33:57,511
the smell of the shallot.

373
00:33:59,581 --> 00:34:03,383
This will make it taste better.

374
00:34:10,414 --> 00:34:11,927
Could you slice and look at the camera?

375
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:14,041
With confidence.

376
00:34:19,981 --> 00:34:21,782
Are you even a real chef?

377
00:34:29,824 --> 00:34:31,926
Can I get a confident expression?

378
00:34:37,965 --> 00:34:39,333
Look at the camera too, this one.

379
00:34:41,202 --> 00:34:43,437
Ah, and slice, you have to slice too.

380
00:34:49,610 --> 00:34:50,912
Blood!

381
00:34:54,482 --> 00:34:56,082
- Tao Sor!
- Come here.

382
00:34:56,083 --> 00:34:57,318
Is it serious?

383
00:34:58,019 --> 00:35:00,955
- Daiji, go get the first aid kit
- Okay.

384
00:35:07,895 --> 00:35:09,462
Does it hurt alot?

385
00:35:09,463 --> 00:35:10,503
Hold on for a while, okay?

386
00:35:27,633 --> 00:35:28,293
You're good?

387
00:35:32,239 --> 00:35:32,973
Tao Sor.

388
00:35:33,147 --> 00:35:34,314
Go rest first.

389
00:35:34,581 --> 00:35:36,141
We'll have Daiji take care of the rest.

390
00:35:36,830 --> 00:35:37,830
Hey man.

391
00:35:38,238 --> 00:35:39,272
It's just a little cut.

392
00:35:40,386 --> 00:35:41,653
I think Tao Sor's still got it.

393
00:35:41,701 --> 00:35:42,769
- Right?
- Hey.

394
00:35:43,864 --> 00:35:45,565
What's your deal with Tao Sor?

395
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:48,881
Are you okay?

396
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:54,795
Yeah, everything is okay.

397
00:35:58,717 --> 00:35:59,351
You know.

398
00:35:59,729 --> 00:36:04,752
We actually came here to be taught cooking by you.

399
00:36:06,706 --> 00:36:11,178
We were actually here last year, try your food, it was incredible, it was amazing.

400
00:36:11,825 --> 00:36:15,161
So, we wanted to come back again and cook with you.

401
00:36:16,162 --> 00:36:19,766
Yeah, I just wanted to cook some nice food for my boyfriend.

402
00:36:20,853 --> 00:36:24,223
Do you remember last year when he complimented you?

403
00:36:32,885 --> 00:36:36,089
You don't remember, do you?

404
00:36:38,163 --> 00:36:39,864
It was only last year when we came.

405
00:36:46,599 --> 00:36:50,803
I think everything is fine, it's okay.

406
00:36:51,141 --> 00:36:52,475
He can continue teaching you.

407
00:36:52,506 --> 00:36:56,709
And he remember you. Let's continue with the Padme Hokkien.

408
00:36:57,631 --> 00:36:58,631
Next time, could you just

409
00:36:58,939 --> 00:37:00,708
go with the flow first, understand?

410
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:06,085
Let me take a photo for you, cooking together.

411
00:37:11,252 --> 00:37:12,319
Daiji.

412
00:37:13,154 --> 00:37:16,157
I think Tao Sor's had enough, take him to rest.

413
00:37:16,490 --> 00:37:17,663
Okay, come!

414
00:37:25,999 --> 00:37:27,300
Apologies.

415
00:37:27,807 --> 00:37:30,610
The chef is not usually be like this.

416
00:37:31,524 --> 00:37:33,960
Maybe he is not feeling well today.

417
00:37:37,730 --> 00:37:40,031
Tell you clients they can order anything

418
00:37:40,149 --> 00:37:41,423
I'll take care of the charges.

419
00:37:42,436 --> 00:37:45,252
As for the contract, I still cannot sign it.

420
00:37:47,088 --> 00:37:50,091
I told you from the beginning that our chef wasn't ready.

421
00:38:11,324 --> 00:38:12,892
Hey.

422
00:38:13,892 --> 00:38:15,014
What are you doing here alone?

423
00:38:15,321 --> 00:38:16,523
Don't you have class?

424
00:38:17,932 --> 00:38:18,818
I went already.

425
00:38:19,164 --> 00:38:20,731
Such a waste of time, learning who knows what.

426
00:38:20,801 --> 00:38:22,708
Better to use the time making content.

427
00:38:23,068 --> 00:38:24,470
What about you? What are you doing?

428
00:38:25,991 --> 00:38:27,793
I'm just ...

429
00:38:28,996 --> 00:38:30,030
..taking a stroll.

430
00:38:30,684 --> 00:38:32,319
Just taking a stroll.

431
00:38:34,535 --> 00:38:36,270
That was bad acting.

432
00:38:39,699 --> 00:38:41,267
Like you'd know.

433
00:38:42,977 --> 00:38:44,545
It's just..

434
00:38:45,198 --> 00:38:46,667
I don't wann go back home yet.

435
00:38:47,648 --> 00:38:49,449
I don't wanna deal with Sang's questions.

436
00:38:49,450 --> 00:38:51,151
Which means,

437
00:38:51,152 --> 00:38:54,154
today's trip wasn't good.

438
00:38:54,155 --> 00:38:55,389
Aren't I right.

439
00:38:57,063 --> 00:38:59,933
I shouldn't have went with that Precious Resort.

440
00:39:01,307 --> 00:39:02,442
That Chef Tao Sor,

441
00:39:03,572 --> 00:39:05,573
his skills are good, that's true

442
00:39:05,598 --> 00:39:06,866
but unprofessional.

443
00:39:07,613 --> 00:39:08,613
Chef Tao Sor...

444
00:39:09,349 --> 00:39:12,272
Oh! The youngest son of The Pitch or something?

445
00:39:12,973 --> 00:39:15,141
I've heard people talk,

446
00:39:15,142 --> 00:39:18,144
that the youngest son had disappeared for a while.

447
00:39:18,145 --> 00:39:19,546
And once he came back,

448
00:39:19,547 --> 00:39:21,115
he didn't really go anywhere.

449
00:39:22,708 --> 00:39:24,543
Some people have also said

450
00:39:25,024 --> 00:39:26,292
he was harrased.

451
00:39:26,869 --> 00:39:28,888
Other people say,

452
00:39:29,248 --> 00:39:30,449
he drowned.

453
00:39:32,151 --> 00:39:33,886
Until his brain wasn't normal.

454
00:39:35,976 --> 00:39:38,874
But, no one's ever confirmed what the real story is

455
00:39:38,899 --> 00:39:41,902
and his family doesn't say much either.

456
00:39:43,871 --> 00:39:45,206
Really?

457
00:39:50,811 --> 00:39:53,246
Would you want to get your fortune told?

458
00:39:53,247 --> 00:39:55,748
Your business might blow up, you know.

459
00:39:55,749 --> 00:39:57,750
No, that's enough.

460
00:39:57,751 --> 00:40:00,954
Just being trapped her for a year because of a feng shui master's tellings

461
00:40:01,307 --> 00:40:03,242
it's already driving me crazy.

462
00:40:03,850 --> 00:40:06,402
- Stop. With the fortune tellers, stop
- Listen first!

463
00:40:06,427 --> 00:40:08,414
This one's for real, I gurantee.

464
00:40:08,481 --> 00:40:11,484
- No, no
- Hey!

465
00:40:13,067 --> 00:40:16,503
That's why his luck's down, he hasn't even checked it yet.

466
00:40:52,164 --> 00:40:53,933
Look, you.

467
00:40:55,255 --> 00:40:56,990
Why are you sitting here alone?

468
00:41:01,127 --> 00:41:03,930
I’m just sitting here watching the sunset.

469
00:41:40,189 --> 00:41:41,309
Are you afraid of the ocean?

470
00:41:45,021 --> 00:41:48,089
'll bring you out there. Trust me.

471
00:41:53,509 --> 00:41:55,277
I've never been in the ocean before.

472
00:41:58,001 --> 00:42:01,972
In that case, there might be another way.

473
00:42:16,693 --> 00:42:20,363
I’ll be the one who becomes your memory
